cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL

This paper is about machine reading of biomedical literature, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL). Among these, cs.CL and cs.IR are the most likely categories as they directly relate to the paper's focus on natural language processing and information retrieval. The paper also mentions the use of reinforcement learning, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL).
